text: Non-abelian or nonabelian may refer to: * Non-abelian group, in mathematics, a group that is not abelian (commutative) * Non-abelian gauge theory, in physics, a gauge group that is non-abelian ==See also== * Non-abelian gauge transformation, a gauge transformation * Non-abelian class field theory, in class field theory * Nonabelian cohomology, a cohomology * Abelian (disambiguation) *
title: Non-abelian
